      englishText: 'O Allah, Knower of the unseen and the seen, Creator of the heavens and earth, Lord and Master of all things. I bear witness that none has the right to be worshipped but You. I seek refuge in You from the evil of my soul and from the evil of Satan.',
      frenchText: "\u00d4 Allah, Connaisseur de l'invisible et du visible, Cr\u00e9ateur des cieux et de la terre, Seigneur et Ma\u00eetre de toute chose. J'atteste que nul ne m\u00e9rite d'\u00eatre ador\u00e9 sauf Toi. Je cherche refuge aupr\u00e8s de Toi contre le mal de mon \u00e2me et contre le mal de Satan.",
      transliteration: "Allaahumma 'aalimal-ghaybi wash-shahaadah, faatiras-samaawaati wal-ard, Rabba kulli shay'in wa maleekah, ash-hadu al-laa ilaaha illaa Ant. A'oodhu bika min sharri nafsee wa min sharrish-shaytaani wa shirkihi.",
