      englishText: 'In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful. 112:1 Say, He is Allah, [who is] One. 112:2 Allah, the Eternal Refuge. 112:3 He neither begets nor is born. 112:4 Nor is there to Him any equivalent.',
